          <tr><td>Surface igniter electrode (single)</td><td>$185 – $275</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Gas valve assembly (single burner)</td><td>$425 – $640</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Burner tube (single)</td><td>$165 – $240</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Burner cap (single)</td><td>$65 – $95</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Oven igniter (all-gas, glow-bar)</td><td>$245 – $340</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Bake element (dual-fuel)</td><td>$225 – $325</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Broil element</td><td>$245 – $345</td></tr>
          <tr><td>RTD temperature probe</td><td>$165 – $245</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Convection fan motor (dual-fuel)</td><td>$285 – $420</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Oven door hinge (single)</td><td>$185 – $265</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Oven door hinge (pair, recommended)</td><td>$340 – $485</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Oven door gasket</td><td>$285 – $420</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Glass door inner pane</td><td>$345 – $520</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Electronic Oven Control (EOC) board</td><td>$640 – $920</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Thermostat (legacy ranges)</td><td>$185 – $265</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Control knob (single)</td><td>$45 – $75</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Oven light bulb &amp; socket</td><td>$85 – $125</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Self-clean latch motor</td><td>$195 – $285</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Range-hood fan motor (paired ventilation)</td><td>$285 – $385</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Preventive maintenance visit</td><td>$145 flat</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── WARRANTY ── -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow-sub">Warranty context</p>
      <h2>Viking range warranty and when to call us</h2>
      <p>Viking residential range warranty is <strong>3 years on all parts and labor</strong>, one of the more generous in the premium segment. During the warranty window, call Viking at <strong>1-888-845-4641</strong> for Viking Certified Service dispatch at no parts cost.</p>
      <p>Post-warranty is where we operate. Most of our Viking range calls are 4-to-20-year-old units where the warranty has closed. Same factory training, faster response, lower labor rate than a post-warranty Viking Certified dispatch. For integrated Viking kitchens (range + fridge + grill + hood), we service all categories on a single dispatch, see our <a href="/brands/viking/">Viking hub</a> for the full scope.</p>
      <p>Viking range sealed-burner gas components are covered only under the base 3-year warranty; there's no extended sealed-system coverage equivalent to the 12-year refrigeration warranty. This matters for repair-vs-replace decisions on 15+ year old ranges where major gas valve or manifold work would be needed.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── SERVICE AREAS ── -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow-sub">Where we go</p>
      <h2>Service areas for Viking range repair</h2>
      <BrandBranchesGrid showHeader={false} />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── RELATED ── -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow-sub">Related Viking services</p>
      <h2>Other Viking categories we service</h2>
      <div class="cat-grid">
        <a href="/brands/viking/" class="cat-card">
          <h3>Viking Appliance Repair</h3>
          <p>Hub page, all Viking categories across Southern California including refrigerator, grill, oven, cooktop, hood.</p>
          <span class="cat-cta">View hub →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/brands/viking-refrigerator-repair/" class="cat-card">
          <h3>Viking Refrigerator Repair</h3>
          <p>7 Series built-in, Professional columns, wine coolers, undercounter. 12-year sealed-system warranty awareness.</p>
          <span class="cat-cta">View refrigerator repair →</span>
